%2F%2Fi.kinja-img.com%2Fgawker-media%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fatubqn5pkjlbk2bgrvbe.jpg&h=7178818f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此季將延續第六季的結尾，當救世軍領袖尼根一棒殺死瑞克組群中的其中一人的時刻；本季將講述瑞克一行人受到史無前例的威脅下而被迫妥協，但在暗中也開始與敵人做鬥爭。而多個漫畫角色也即將在本季現身，其中包括漫畫裏的核心角色&mdash;以西結，與他身邊所養的大老虎「希瓦」。本季也即將增加幾個新場所，救世軍總部「聖殿」與以西結的「神之國」。"},{"pid":"ce22efc6b1c003b427680c8f8bd82cbe4206d211","tid":344842,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d3284efa3a1003052252cc4b477a0858ef598a","tid":344842,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01e51cd3105c267a5417b9c6242a27cd9a2cb2c","tid":344842,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fd3ba0ba5231bdbb5f5a49f339d4bb2e41369a","tid":344842,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622d86bca0d9a63033863bc4f9e39918c9bf0185","tid":344842,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442a322f1c60fced61d8a80523ce1a31d1d1ff58","tid":344842,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T17:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\